# csshX

> Cluster SSH tool for macOS
> More information: https://github.com/brockgr/csshx

- Connect to multiple hosts:

`csshX {string value: hostname1} {string value: hostname2}`

- Connect to multiple hosts with a given SSH key:

`csshX {string value: user@hostname1} {string value: user@hostname2} --ssh_args "-i {string value: path/to/ssh_key.pem}"`

- Connect to a pre-defined cluster from `/etc/clusters`:

`csshX cluster1`
